flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: New carrier bid submission, contract renewal event, or flagged lane capacity/coverage gap.]
  A --> N1[Stream: DDM/Crawlers - Ingest carrier bids, contracts, lane schedules, and historical performance into the DI platform]
  N1 --> N2[Stream: STREAMS - Normalize and score carriers on cost, SLA compliance, integration readiness, and historical performance]
  N2 --> N3{PB: Process Builder (Rules + IF + Branch) - Apply deterministic selection rules and business policies to pick primary and backup carriers; surface exceptions}
  N3 -->|Primary| N4[PB: Remote Functions - Execute onboarding and system integration tasks; write selected carrier, contract and rate cards into SAP S/4HANA]
  N4 --> N5[PB: CWB Lifecycle - Govern ongoing performance and escalate SLA breaches or contract deviations to stakeholders]
  N5 --> N6[UI: UI Screen / Dashboard - Surface selection outcomes, onboarding status, and carrier KPIs to procurement and operations dashboards]
  N6 --> Z1[Outcome: Reduced freight COGS, improved on-time delivery performance (OTIF), stronger working capital via better transport efficiency, faster carrier onboarding, and continuous performance governance.]
  N3 -->|Carrier fails integration readiness c...| B1[Create onboarding action item and schedule integration project; fallback to backup carrier if lane critical]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Onboarding queued with estimated lead time; critical shipments routed to compliant carriers to avoid disruption]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Bid price exceeds cost threshold or v...| B2[Auto-reject or flag for procurement negotiation via Action Item and Notification; optionally re-run selection with alternative carriers]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Procurement engages carrier for re-bid or rejects; cost outliers prevented from entering execution]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Carrier score indicates high SLA risk...| B3[Block auto-selection, route to CWB Lifecycle for review and require remediation plan before onboarding]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Protects OTIF and reduces downstream disruption; high-risk carriers placed on watchlist until improved]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]